sentences: Heba Kadry is an Egyptian mastering engineer who currently resides in Brooklyn, New York.
She is best known for her work with Bjork, Beach House, Slowdive, The Mars Volta, Neon Indian, Wooden Shjips, Lightning Bolt, White Hills, Alex G, Future Islands, Liturgy, !!!
Kadry worked as a staff engineer at SugarHill Recording Studios from 2005 to 2006.
